$_['task_1_desc'] = '
<p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">A Domain Name is the URL of your site that you type in your browser to access the website and replaces the IP address because of the difficulty of maintaining the IP for each site. An example of the domain name is&nbsp;<a href="https://www.google.com/" target="_self" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">google.com</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href="https://www.expandcart.com/en/" target="_self" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">expandcart.com</a>, and the domain is unique to your website only and different from any other website, there are no homes with the same address!</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>1. What is the importance of registering a domain name?</strong></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">When you sign up on the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.expandcart.com/en/" target="_self" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">ExpandCart</a>&nbsp;platform, you get a control panel and a storefront that contains all the data for the store. This is known as hosting, but in this case, your store is displayed as a sub-domain of the expandcart.com domain for example abc.expandcart.com</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">To create a custom name instead of this address you must register what is known as a domain name to replace abc.expandcart.com to be something like mystoreabc.com, that will allow you to have a dedicated domain name and a business identity on the Internet.</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>2. Tips for choosing a domain name</strong></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">- Your domain name should be easy to type<br>- The name of your domain should be as short as possible (between a word or two)<br>- Your domain name may contain some of the keywords relevant to your business<br>- Stay away from the Arabic domains always make sure to choose English domains<br>- Your domain name may contain the name of the country or something like "sa", "eg", etc.<br>- We recommend that you stay away from symbols in choosing a domain for your store<br>- Make sure to choose an attractive and wonderful domain for your store<br>- We recommend that all available domain extensions be purchased for the same domain name</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>3. If I already have a domain, how do I link it to my online store in expandcart?</strong></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">To connect your domain to your store without having to transfer the domain to us, following these steps:</p><ol style="padding-left: 20px; list-style-position: outside; margin: 20px 0px 20px 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><li>Log on to your domain account</li><li>Enter into&nbsp;<strong>DNS</strong>&nbsp;settings</li><li>Create the following two<strong>&nbsp;A Records</strong></li></ol><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">With the following data</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Host: @</strong></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Points to / IP: 35.246.252.14</strong></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Host: www</strong></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Points to / IP: 35.246.252.14</strong></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Then you add the domain in the control panel, you can add up to 3 domains per store</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">Store Settings &gt;&gt; Domains &gt;&gt; Write a new domain name and then click on Add Domain Link</p>

';

