<p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><a href="https://www.expandcart.com/en" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">E</a><a href="https://www.expandcart.com/en" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">xpandCart</a>&nbsp;is enriched by carefully designed templates that are suitable for any business and built using the latest technologies to provide the best shopping experience for your customers.</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><br></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Designs for Every Business:&nbsp;</strong>Whatever you are selling, you will find awesome designs suitable for you. to explore and choose theme click <a href="/admin/setting/template" target="_blank">here</a>.</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Fully Responsive Templates:</strong>&nbsp;Fully responsive templates that look good on all devices starting from the homepage to checkout.</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Amazing Shopping Experience For Mobile Users:</strong>&nbsp;More than 50% of online customers are using smartphones to browse and buy. You will provide a unique shopping experience for them starting from fully responsive templates that work great on all devices to a customized mobile app for your store.</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Live Customization:</strong>&nbsp;A magic tool to help you customize any theme in REAL-TIME. When changing settings of any parameter, you will see how your front-page works. You can also edit the rest of the settings in a clear and easy tabbed template customization page. to access the tool click <a href="/admin/teditor/teditor" target="_blank">here</a>.</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Custom Designs. From Our Experts:</strong>&nbsp;Our experts will help you customize your templates, starting from on-the-spot design customization to complete web, images, and logo design services. Request a quote from our support after registration.</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Language templates design:</strong>&nbsp;All the solutions we provide naively supports Arabic and English languages, and you can always add more languages as you need.</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>You can see the following videos that were created to help you design the store</strong></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><a href="https://youtu.be/e2XbeAq2xJg" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">https://youtu.be/e2XbeAq2xJg</a></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><a href="https://youtu.be/qFFT-AZMMWQ" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">https://youtu.be/qFFT-AZMMWQ</a></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><a href="https://youtu.be/bynkPEUAoK4" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">https://youtu.be/bynkPEUAoK4</a></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><strong>We also invite you to enter the following link to view and read many articles that highlight the templates and design</strong></p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><a href="https://support.expandcart.com/hc/en/categories/360000924714-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B5%D9%85%D9%8A%D9%85-" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">https://support.expandcart.com/hc/en/categories/360000924714</a></p>
