<h2 style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal;"><a href="https://www.expandcart.com/en/" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">ExpandCart</span></a><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;platform Add a variety of shipping methods inside the store control panel to facilitate the work of preparing the shipment products to your store customers.</span></h2><h2><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;">To access Shipping Setting Click <a href="/admin/extension/shipping" target="_blank">Here</a></p></h2><h2 style="font-family: Montserrat, Cairo, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.53846; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;">Shipping categories were divided into 3 categories:</p></h2><h2><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;">Custom Shipping Costs, Shipment Delivery Companies, Manual Delivery</p><p style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;"><strong style="font-size: 18px;">1. Custom Shipping Costs</strong><br></p></h2><h3 style="margin-top: 0px;"><p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal;">Custom Flat Rate, Custom Cost per Geo Zone &amp; Weight, Custom Flat Rate per Product, Free Shipping, Category &amp; Product-Based Shipping</p><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: normal;"><strong style="font-size: 15px;">Custom Flat Rate</strong></div><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">Through this method, you can set a fixed shipping rate for each order at your store</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;products so that a certain fixed price can be fixed for all the products of the store and these products are shipped to any place at this fixed price</span></div><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: normal;"><strong style="font-size: 15px;"><br></strong></div><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: normal;"><strong style="font-size: 15px;">Custom Cost per Geo Zone &amp; Weight</strong></div><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: normal;"><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">Through this method, you can set a custom shipping rate for each geographical area and you can change this price with the weight product changes. Where you can inside this setting method add the shipping price and next to it the product weight, like the following examples:</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">50-500:5&nbsp; ,&nbsp; 600-1000:10,&nbsp; &nbsp;1100-1500:15</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><strong><br></strong></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><strong>Custom Flat Rate per Product</strong></p></div><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: normal;"><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">In this way you can set a fixed shipping price to be applied to each product added to the cart, meaning that each product added to the cart will be added the price of shipping it,,, as an example if the price of shipping&nbsp;<strong>10$</strong>&nbsp;per product and added to the cart purchase<strong>&nbsp;3 Products</strong>&nbsp;will be shipping cost&nbsp;<strong>30$</strong></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><strong><br></strong><strong>Free Shipping</strong></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">In this way, you can make free shipping available to your store at product order, as when the total order amount of the product may exceed a certain amount with the possibility of determining the geographical area which will be characterized by free shipping</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">For example, when the total amount of products in the purchasing cart is&nbsp;<strong>100$</strong>&nbsp;with the country&nbsp; Jordan the shipping is free.</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><strong><br></strong></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><strong>Category &amp; Product-Based Shipping</strong></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">This method of shipping is one of the most shipping methods that contain many characteristics and conditions that can be used on a section, product, geographical area, total purchase cart and other conditions that can be added</p></div><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: normal;"></div></h3><h3 style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal;"><strong>2. Manual Delivery</strong></h3><h3 style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal;"><strong><br></strong><strong style="font-size: 15px;">Pickup From Store</strong></h3><h3 style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal;"><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">Through this way, you can enable buyers to save the cost and time of delivery by receiving the products themselves from your local store,,,</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">In order to do this you only you need to enable the status and choose the Geo Zone which this shipping method will apply and then press&nbsp;<strong>Save</strong></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><br></p></h3><h3 style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal;"><strong>3. Shipping companies</strong></h3><h3 style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal;"><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;">There are four shipping companies have been contracted and merged with them to allow our customers to make accounts on them and then add this accounts in any way of shipping, they are the most famous shipping companies:</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://www.aramex.com/" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">Aramex</a></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://www.ups.com/us/en/Home.page" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">UPS</a></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://www.fedex.com/global/choose-location.html" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">FedEx</a></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><a href="http://www.smsaexpress.com/index.html" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">Simsa Express</a></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://www.dhl.com/en.html" target="_self" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">DHL</a></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://www.dhl.com/en/express.html" target="_self" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);"><span class="wysiwyg-underline" style="text-decoration-line: underline;">DHL Express</span></a></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><a href="http://salasa.co/ar/" target="_self" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">Salasa</a></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><a href="http://zajilship.com/" target="_self" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">zajil</a></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><strong>For more information on how to create an account at one of these companies please read the following article&nbsp;</strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://support.expandcart.com/hc/en-us/articles/360005046754" style="color: rgb(2, 99, 143);">https://support.expandcart.com/hc/en-us/articles/360005046754</a>&nbsp;</p></h3>
';

